    "desc": "Use the AudioNames platform to record, share, and embed your audio name pronunciation with a bio profile to build personal branding in minutes.",
    "navbar": "Why Audionames\nPlatform\nDictionary\nPricing\nSign Up\nDear Guest\nSign up or Login",
    "text": "Why Audionames\nPlatform\nDictionary\nPricing\nSign Up\nDear Guest\nSign up or Login\nYour Name Pronunciation is the\nNew Powerful Marketing Tool\nConnect prospects easily and personally anywhere and everywhere. AudioNames lets you build a personal branding for your digital identity to pitch yourself and generate more leads.\nBuild Your Name Page Now\nFree forever | Set up in minutes | No credit card required\nBusiness Card\nContactless Card\nMessengers\nRecord, display, and share your name pronunciation anywhere.\nUserfriendly and super simple to set up and use\nPersonalized\nAdd all of your links, how your name is pronounced, and a bio about you into a single page with AudioNames.\nUnique and Powerful\nFully customizable templates with custom colors, fonts, and images. Can use your own domain.\nManage Easily\nCreate and update your personal website in minutes. No download or design skills are needed!\nQuick and Easy to Share\nThe only link you'll need to share online and offline too!\nDesigned to be personal.\nGreat for your entire business team.\nPersonal Website\nPersonal Website\nUse your AudioNames pronunciation and bio profile to create your highly impressive personal website in less than five minutes.\nREPLACES:\nBio Link Solution\nEmail Signature\nDigital Business Card\nWidgets\nTeam Showcase\nPortal\nHosted About Us Page\nLead Capture Forms\nThere are so many ways you can use AudioNames\nDigital Business Card\nBio Link\nLead Generation Tool\nLink To Any URL\nInstagram\nTik tok\nTwitter\nEmail\nYoutube\nFacebook\nWebsite\nBlog\nMessenger\nSpotify\nPinterest\nLinkedIn\nCrowdsourced\nNames Pronunciation Dictionary\nPut an end to the mispronunciation of anyone's name instantly.\nShare your knowledge and help others.\nLook It Up\nContribute\nEarn IQ\nCertificate\nPractice Mode\nRequest\nLook It Up\nTo find the correct pronunciation of anyone's name. Type the full name and click on the audio icon to learn instantly.\nBuild personal branding,\nGrow your online presence &\nAchieve your marketing goals.\nBrand Your Name Now\nFree forever. Set up in minutes. No credit card required.\nTestimonials\nCase Studies\nReviews\nby JDify\nYour name pronunciation & personal branding made easy\nSelf-Serve Resources\nHelp center\nWhat’s new\nAcademy\nBlog\nProduct Support Team\nSupport ticket\nLive chat\nStatus\nWall of love\nRequest a feature\nProduct roadmap\nAudioNames Blogs\nHave More Questions?\nWe're always happy to help.\nContact us !\nFeatures\nDictionary\nAbout\nTerms\nPrivacy\n© 2022 AudioNames. A\nJDify\nProduct.\nMake everyone pronounce your name by recording, showing, and sharing your name pronunciation anywhere.\nPronounce you’re most influential Identity, The Name right, and design your own customizable and personalized Site, E-Business Card & Email Signature with various AudioNames features, and know your team in Team Showcase. Create a personalized website with custom domain name and share your personal website link to any individual or on any social media platform. Acquire high-quality leads and prospects for your business by promoting your personal brand.",
